<p><a name="Screenplay" id="Screenplay"></a></p>
<h4><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Mamoru_Oshii&amp;action=edit&amp;section=19" title="Edit section: Screenplay">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Screenplay</span></h4>
<ul>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Dallos" title="Dallos">Dallos</a></i> (1983)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Urusei_Yatsura_2:_Beautiful_Dreamer" title="Urusei Yatsura 2: Beautiful Dreamer" class="mw-redirect">Urusei Yatsura 2: Beautiful Dreamer</a></i> (1984)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Angel%27s_Egg" title="Angel's Egg">Angel's Egg</a></i> (1985)</li>
